{"tid":90410,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"呢世人唔會再返中學母校","createTime":"2017-01-22T05:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T18:11:51.000Z","uid":45772,"like":65,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f79dbfbad21b62e8e5143b5af6165ccbb41d0233","tid":90410,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:29:48.000Z","msg":"呢世人唔會再返中學母校 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚憎母校 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea2bcf7f6977d6f2699b82b7fef4585edad207a","tid":90410,"uid":3510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:30:17.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"75e8779bc200bc48581f74934718cfd09dcd1597","tid":90410,"uid":22387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:33:34.000Z","msg":"唔洗咁激動既<br />\n我對母校無乜感情（有少少憎）<br />\n咪一樣畢左業咁耐都冇返過去<br />\n出到黎做野之後你會發現以前好多野都係小事黎<br />\n因為社會大學舊屎仲難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4573d43470d66134be3c5785b8eae02e567ecb2c","tid":90410,"uid":18794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:40:04.000Z","msg":"無野值得留戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1154ce496e0218345ad72671b654780299c9e425","tid":90410,"uid":66527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:31:14.000Z","msg":"仆街母校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比左咁多年苦我受 呢加仲有手尾跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade10b7373d6298c6232faa74e22cbfa1eb22392","tid":90410,"uid":52874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:17:32.000Z","msg":"中學母校？不了"},{"pid":"c4d805d6f6e2b4547e801509ab33f2547d078fa0","tid":90410,"uid":64114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T02:31:00.000Z","msg":"第一間中學垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n知我轉校就扮大牌打黎摧尻我轉校 <br />\n語氣又勁撚差咁 <br />\n心諗收皮啦 <br />\n依家係我要走唔係你踢我出校呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c141bbcd03bfbf075753365692b74c742a730228","tid":90410,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T02:34:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗咁激動既<br />\n我對母校無乜感情（有少少憎）<br />\n咪一樣畢左業咁耐都冇返過去<br />\n出到黎做野之後你會發現以前好多野都係小事黎<br />\n因為社會大學舊屎仲難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無錯， 人大左就自然現出面既屎難食十萬倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6665d1f01a66cee82a9dbdcf7c6a6dbb86cf2dc","tid":90410,"uid":48189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T02:50:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"939582a4b5031dfb36334cc0e4febb2fa35e4537","tid":90410,"uid":76505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:04:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49988f96d1ce5fc0203164cbce4326e9e6f48d32","tid":90410,"uid":34336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:08:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01b8500d6eb85d2cfd4097d95a777bf98f64c8bb","tid":90410,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:12:07.000Z","msg":"我畢業之後第一次返母校個時<br />\n係母校殺校<br />\n自己做建築公司，接到拆母校tender個時<br />\n報tender前既site inspection<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3dc086d574d81514735c8ead662f61965ca3ddd","tid":90410,"uid":35315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:22:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我畢業之後第一次返母校個時<br />\n係母校殺校<br />\n自己做建築公司，